Enum Action

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Action>
      • thinktank.javabot.intelligences.Action
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Action>

    public enum Action
extends java.lang.Enum<Action>
    Enumération des actions pouvant être choisies par les scripts IA: -noAction: The no action. -moveForward: The move forward. -moveBackward: The move backward. -turnClockwise: The turn clockwise. -turnCounterClockwise: The turn counter clockwise. -shoot: The shoot. -scriptCompleted: The script Completed. -scriptTerminated: The script Terminated.
    Author:
    MOTEZ
